{"tid":795152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"完全接受唔到女人八字腳行路","createTime":"2018-08-26T18:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T03:52:10.000Z","uid":5949,"like":45,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"436c5290ed0b5060926e0cd2b61933cf459b49f5","tid":795152,"uid":5949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"話說行街嘅時候都會留意前面嘅人行路方式<br />\n發現好多人都會有八字腳行路嘅習慣<br />\n再望一望佢哋嘅樣同打扮<br />\n又覺得佢哋幾正常 有啲甚至可以話係高質<br />\n但係見到佢哋咁樣行路就覺得好辛苦<br />\n之後我再觀察<br />\n發覺好多都係後生仔女嚟<br />\n我有時真係忍唔住會想行過去同佢哋講<br />\n叫佢哋行好啲<br />\n因為無論係外八定內八都真係好核突<br />\n甚至我覺得有啲影響市容<br />\n係咪我諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：個人幾靚幾正都好，八字腳行路就影衰晒成個人嘅形象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：人哋點樣行路關你咩事"},{"pid":"9cfdf3957b46cfc2e47c4f35e230b253c25b5d0b","tid":795152,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:17:12.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"c59ebf4316a95b46dfedfac466c32ec10ca5d7b1","tid":795152,"uid":5949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cfdf3957b46cfc2e47c4f35e230b253c25b5d0b","tid":795152,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:17:12.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"真係好鬼核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲後生女行路行到成個啊嬋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382ea6afb0ff95167426042a6e67f847e9e60c48","tid":795152,"uid":1590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"衣家啲人唔會再教小朋友禮儀、儀態"},{"pid":"69475d3bc2ed51997c7cbdca3d744fff7cc89a38","tid":795152,"uid":5949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"382ea6afb0ff95167426042a6e67f847e9e60c48","tid":795152,"uid":1590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"衣家啲人唔會再教